# drizzle — DO NOT IGNORE.
# Migration files and the journal must be tracked in git; otherwise the prod
# `pnpm db:migrate` step on Vercel runs against an empty migrations folder and
# silently skips schema changes. See docs/MIGRATIONS.md.

